<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695373' id='t-695373'>AAA: You see, undercover is always a last resort.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698563' id='t-698563'>Before we go undercover, we follow the rules.</span>
