<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722716' id='t-722716'>I'm okay, I go in. Risky, yes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='724804' id='t-724804'>but it's a hazard of a profession.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='727460' id='t-727460'>I mean, everybody has their hazard.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729013' id='t-729013'>And once you say that is yours,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730946' id='t-730946'>you've got to take it, as and when it comes.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
